%% E039 - ParserWorker flow - F1-3 Pipeline CSJN
%% Source: docs/design/f1-3-parser.md (E038), architecture 3.2.2, 3.4
sequenceDiagram
    participant QP as queue-parser
    participant PW as ParserWorker
    participant API as CSJN API
    participant Blob as Blob Storage
    participant QE as queue-enrichment

    QP->>PW: ParserMessage (documentId, analysisId, blobPathPdf, contentHash)
    PW->>API: GET abrirAnalisis?idAnalisis
    API-->>PW: caseTitle, jurisdiction, resourceType, rulingDirection, etc.
    PW->>API: GET getAllDocumentos?idAnalisis
    API-->>PW: document list
    PW->>API: GET getSumariosAnalisis?idAnalisis
    API-->>PW: keywords, holding, summary
    PW->>API: GET getCitas?idDocumento
    API-->>PW: citations (alias, summaryId)
    PW->>API: GET getCitantes?idDocumento
    API-->>PW: citedBy (analysisId, caseNumber)
    PW->>Blob: Get PDF stream (blobPathPdf)
    Blob-->>PW: PDF binary
    Note over PW: PdfPig extract + normalize text
    PW->>PW: Merge API responses into ExtractedMetadata
    PW->>PW: Calculate missingFields
    PW->>QE: EnrichmentMessage (extractedMetadata, normalizedText, missingFields)
